<% layout("layouts/boilerplate") %>

<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">

  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="mb-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800">Terms & Conditions</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">
      Last updated: April 2026
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Content -->
  <div class="bg-white border rounded-xl shadow-sm p-6 space-y-6 text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">1. Platform Usage</h2>
      <p class="mt-2">
        MediCycle provides a marketplace for connecting buyers and sellers of medical batches.
        By using this platform, you agree to use it only for lawful purposes.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">2. User Roles</h2>
      <p class="mt-2">
        Users are classified as buyers or sellers. Sellers can list medical batches, while buyers can place orders.
        Each role has specific permissions within the system.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">3. Account Responsibility</h2>
      <p class="mt-2">
        You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account credentials.
        Any activity performed under your account will be considered your responsibility.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">4. Orders & Transactions</h2>
      <p class="mt-2">
        Orders placed through the platform are subject to seller acceptance.
        MediCycle does not directly handle physical delivery or external logistics.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">5. Pricing & Listings</h2>
      <p class="mt-2">
        Sellers are responsible for ensuring accurate pricing, batch details, and availability.
        MediCycle is not liable for incorrect or outdated listings.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">6. Prohibited Activities</h2>
      <p class="mt-2">
        Users must not engage in fraudulent activity, misuse the platform, or attempt unauthorized access to other accounts or data.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p class="mt-2">
        MediCycle is not responsible for any direct or indirect damages arising from the use of the platform.
        Users operate at their own risk.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">8. Modifications</h2>
      <p class="mt-2">
        We reserve the right to update these terms at any time. Continued use of the platform implies acceptance of updated terms.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">9. Contact</h2>
      <p class="mt-2">
        For questions regarding these terms, contact:
        <span class="font-medium text-gray-900">support@medicycle.com</span>
      </p>
    </section>

  </div>

</div>